<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.3">
<l>vaiyamel lāmpeṟum vārkaṭal vāḻum</l>
<l rend="indent">makarak kuḻaikoṇṭu vaittēṉ</l>
<l>veyyavē kātil tiriyai yiṭuvaṉnī</l>
<l rend="indent">vēṇṭiya tellān taruva</l>
<l>ṉuyyaviv vāyar kulattiṉil tōṉṟiya</l>
<l rend="indent">voṇcuṭa rāyar koḻuntē</l>
<l>maiyaṉmai ceytiḷa vāycciya ruḷḷattu</l>
<l rend="indent">mātava ṉēyiṅkē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have brought the earrings[in the shape of] of the makara</l>
<l rend="indent">that live in the vast ocean that bears the entire earth.</l>
<l>[When] I put the thread in your ears [they will become] hot.</l>
<l>I will give you whatever you want.</l>
<l>O sprout of the cowherds, shining light who appeared</l>
<l rend="indent">in this cowherd clan in order to save [them],</l>
<l>O husband of Śrī, creating madness in the hearts of the young cowherdessess,</l>
<l>Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
